IMMEDIATE
No.55/4/CF-66(1)
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA
CABINET SECRETARTAT
(Department of Cabinet Affairs)
New Delhi, the 29th January 1966.
The undersigned is directed to state that the Ministers
and Deputy Ministers, named below, assuned office with effect
from the forenoon of Saturday, January 29, 1966;-
Cabinet Minister
Shri Fakhruddin Ahmed
Minister of Irrigation
& Power.
Minister of State
Shri T.N. Singh
Minister of Iron & Steel.
Deputy Ministers
Deputy Minister in the
Ministry of Information
& Broadcasting.
Shrimati Nandini Satpa thy
Shri Shafi Quareshi
Deputy Minister in the
Ministry of Commerce.
(D.P. Chopra)
for Cabinet Secretary,
To
All Members of the Council of Ministers.
Copy forwarded to the Secretary to the Prime Minister/
the Private Secretary to the Prime Minister, for information.
Copy forwarded to the Secretary to the President/
the Private Secretary to the Vice-President, for information.
(D.P. Chopra)
Under Secretary to the Cabinet.
Copy forwarded to all Secretaries/Special Secretaries/
Additional Secretaries to the Government of India/Chairman,
Rallway Board/Secretary, Election Commission, for information.
Copy forwarded to all Ministries/Departments of the
Government of India/Lok Sabha Secretariat/Rajya Sabha
Secretariat, for information.
(D.P. Chopra)
Under Secretary to the Cabinet.
"JEET"
250 00PIES
